p.d: This monthly magazine is dedicated to the story of Olympic Sailing, as the world’s stars names and best rookies strive to compete on the world’s greatest sports stage and claim their medals at the Olympic Games. To be a champion you need power, strength, skill, mental toughness, supreme tness and strategy. Broadcast by over 20 broadcasters in more than 95 countries, Sailing to Tokyo follows the long journey and dening moments in athletes’ careers as they aspire to make Olympic history.
